    <div class="tile_texts_container">
      <div class="tile_headline">Determine Root Causes to Prevent Re-Occurrences</div>
      <div class="tile_supporting_content">Root causes can be identified by asking “why?”. For every incident or event there is a root cause. Find & address the root cause rather than trying to only fix the result. This week’s Safety Brief is September’s accidents, injuries, and near misses for you to review with your co-workers and post.</div>
